                  <div class="list-post gird row">
                   <div class="course-item col-lg-3 col-md-3 col-sm-3 three">
                    <div class="use-editor post-811 course type-course status-publish hentry clearfix img-type-full-width" id="post-811"> 
                     <h5> <a href="http://metrouni.edu.bd/course/b-sc-engg-in-cse/" title="B.Sc. Engg. in CSE"><i class="iconentypo-book"></i>B.Sc. Engg. in CSE</a> </h5> 
                     <div class="description"> 
                      <p>The B.Sc. Engineering (CSE) programme is a 48(forty-eight)-months study of 12 semesters for regular students. A student should complete at…</p> 
                      <a href="http://metrouni.edu.bd/course/b-sc-engg-in-cse/" class="btn btn-sm btn-color">Read more</a> 
                     </div> 
                    </div>
                   </div> 
                   <div class="course-item col-lg-3 col-md-3 col-sm-3 three">
                    <div class="use-editor post-815 course type-course status-publish hentry clearfix img-type-full-width" id="post-815"> 
                     <h5> <a href="http://metrouni.edu.bd/course/b-sc-engg-in-eee/" title="B.Sc.Engg. in EEE"><i class="iconentypo-book"></i>B.Sc.Engg. in EEE</a> </h5> 
