                          Metropolitan University offers a wide range of services and facilities to the students. The University has excellent environment and facilities such as Library, Labs, Indoor games and Cafeteria. There are many Clubs and Organization which focus to aids students to build a successful career. Students are evolved with club &amp; organization of University which helps them to understand the worth of working together to achieve something. Many Teacher are also involved with these club and organization. Students of different intelligence get chance to shares their own views through the clubs. It creates a nice understanding among the students in the club. Senior students are genuinely shows helpful manner to the juniors eventually it creates a balanced atmosphere in campus. 
