                   <div class="tab-content"> 
                    <div id="tab-54f3adac37d42" tab-id="tab-1" class="tab-pane active">
                     <div class="txt-content"> 
                      <div class="row-wrapper row"> 
                       <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-3 col-sm-3 three"> 
                        <img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1592" alt="ACU" src="http://metrouni.edu.bd/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/ACU2.jpg" width="200" height="133"> 
                        <b>The Association of Commonwealth Universities</b> The Association of Commonwealth Universities (ACU) is the world's first and oldest international university network, established in 1913. ACU has over 500 member institutions in developed and developing countries across the Commonwealth. Metropolitan University has active collaboration with ACU.
                        <b> </b> 
                       </div> 
                       <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-3 col-sm-3 three"> 
                        <img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1595" alt="British" src="http://metrouni.edu.bd/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/British1.jpg" width="200" height="133"> 
                        <b>British Council</b> Metropolitan University has a lively alliance with British Council. Many programs are held in University with their collaboration. Especially the School of Humanities and Social Science has some dynamic activities with British Council. 
                       </div> 
                       <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-3 col-sm-3 three"> 
                        <img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-3040" alt="asic" src="http://metrouni.edu.bd/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/asic.png" width="200" height="133"> 
                        <b>ASIC</b> Internationally recognized agency ‘Accreditation Service for International Schools, Colleges and Universities (ASIC)’ recently added the Metropolitan University, a renowned educational institution of Sylhet in the list of several renowned institutions in the world. 
                       </div> 
                       <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-3 col-sm-3 three"> 
                        <img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1594" alt="BCU" src="http://metrouni.edu.bd/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/BCU1.jpg" width="200" height="133"> 
                        <b>BCU</b> 
                        <em>Birmingham City University</em> and Metropolitan University signed 
                        <em>Memorandum of Understanding</em>. So now it has become easier for students to transfer their credit in Birmingham City University with no trouble. 
                       </div> 
                      </div> 
                     </div>
                    </div> 
