                    <a class="btn btn-sm btn-color" title="CHECK YOUR ADMISSION STATUS" href="http://metrouni.edu.bd/admission-status/"> Click Here</a> 
                   </div> 
                   <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-3 col-sm-3 three"> 
                    <img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-2219" alt="HOLY" src="http://metrouni.edu.bd/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/HOLY.png" width="200" height="133"> 
                    <b>Holidays &amp; Observation</b> Metropolitan University follows Holidays and Observance rules provided by Bangladesh Government. Offices are remained closed during these holidays. 
                    <hr> 
                    <a class="btn btn-sm btn-color" title="SEE AVAILABLE HOLIDAYS" href="http://metrouni.edu.bd/holidays-observation/">Click Here </a> 
                   </div> 
