                    <b>Certificates Verification</b> An academic certification is an official document provided by the University. Click the button to verify your certificates online by providing some required information. 
                    <hr> 
                    <a class="btn btn-sm btn-color" title="VERIFY YOUR CERTIFICATE NOW" href="http://metrouni.edu.bd/certificates-verification/"> Click Here </a> 
                   </div> 
